    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of Abies alba, an ornamental and timber species tree native to the mountainous regions of central and southern Europe and Asia, much used in carpentry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
